# Agent CLI sandbox (Codex hooks + hooks.json under .codex/ — never
# tracked; force-add per-repo with `git add -f .codex/` if a project
# actually wants to track one). `AGENTS.md` is NOT in this block on
# purpose: it's the per-project AI rules file every teammate benefits
# from inheriting on a fresh clone, so it IS tracked.
.codex/

# Test fixture for the NFT picker upload pipeline — replaced on every
# integration test run, never tracked.
backend/internal/ui/static/uploads/

# Literal tilde directory at repo root (dev-sandbox leak). This does
# NOT match the OS home directory — gitignore has no shell expansion;
# `/~/` anchors to a TOP-LEVEL entry literally named `~` only. Per
# project policy this is dev-only on the working machine.
/~/

# Build SHA stamp (generated by CI deploy.yml, compiled into binary)
backend/internal/api/build_sha_gen.go

# Foundry (audit install only — never commit lib/)
contracts/lib/
contracts/foundry.lock
# seed-testnet built binary (run via `go run` from tools/seed-testnet)
tools/seed-testnet/seed-testnet

# NUL device files (Windows artifact)
nul
app/nul
